nodes.text: Zalar Rishek was a young male Human who was a member of the House of Rishek. He attended the launch of the luxury repulsortrain Gem of Alderaan, on Alderaan.

Rishek was spoiled and arrogant, which made him overbearing. He liked to spend his time either chasing potential romantic prospects or racing fast vehicles, such as customized airspeeders, swoops and yachts.
